When this card is Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 "Star Seraph" monster from your hand, then you can place 1 LIGHT monster from your Graveyard on the top of your Deck. An Xyz Monster that was Xyz Summoned using 3 or more monsters you control (including this card on the field) gains this effect.‚óè While this card has Xyz Material, each turn, the first time a monster(s) is Special Summoned from the hand, immediately draw 1 card.
